{"tid":1576986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"部分防暴警無展示警員編號，監警會；暫未接相關投訴","createTime":"2019-09-17T13:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T13:20:23.000Z","uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b81cc248a5f171095256a9d1a57fccae11729d6","tid":1576986,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在監警會的記者會上，對於仍有部分防暴警察無展示警員編號，監警會表示，暫時未有接獲有關的投訴，但相信部分個案可循其他方法核實身份。<br />\n<br />\n監警會主席梁定邦稱：「首先來説沒有人投訴沒有編號，第一我們看不到，但確實有些(投訴)未能提供編號，但他不是投訴沒有編號，現在有很多信息和報道，包括很多角落都有影視，所以只要有時間和地點，比較容易找到那個人。但我不敢說百分之一百，因為就算有肩膀上的警員編號，如果角度不對，都未必一定看到，以及很黑時都未必看到，但現在機會相對高。」"},{"pid":"435d6b86f559902dfbc5f6ad4b54ebb62ea0733d","tid":1576986,"uid":241596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:11:03.000Z","msg":"會員：彭斯 請你收聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568902</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXTR8sf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXTR8sf.jpg&h=2b18572c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ef42dedf3237630ae84900e21cb79a240d1fc87","tid":1576986,"uid":43381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"你含撚啦